title: The Herd-HOUR-1- Porzingis Ejection, Blazers Aren't Normal 8th Seed and Rick Bucher

description:
In Hour-1 of the Podcast, Colin gives his take on the situational awareness, or lack thereof by Kristaps Porzingis. The Portland Trailblazers are unlike Dallas, and are Playoff ready. Rick Bucher also joins to talk about the Lakers struggles and more.
